# WoW MCP First

For this addon workspace, prefer the `wow-api` MCP tools as the primary source for WoW API facts.

- For API/function questions, call `lookup_api` first.
- For discovery/search, call `search_api` before web search.
- For deprecations and replacements, call `list_deprecated`.
- For frame event arguments, call `get_event`.
- For enum constants/values, call `get_enum`.
- For namespace exploration (`C_*`), call `get_namespace`.
- For widget methods (`Frame`, `Button`, etc.), call `get_widget_methods`.

## Reliability order

1. WoW MCP tools
2. Existing project code
3. External docs/web references

If WoW MCP is unavailable, clearly say so and then fall back to other sources.

## Output expectations

- Include exact signatures/parameter names/types when available.
- Call out deprecations and recommended replacements explicitly.
- Prefer Mainline-compatible guidance unless asked otherwise.
